by stof at 2014-06-08T14:07:40Z

@clemens-tolboom The TwigBundle repo does not force you to use dev-master of other repos when using it. It sets its minimum requirement to the actual minimum requirement (i.e. it can work with any HttpKernel since 2.1 according to this constraint)
